 "text": "\n\nFix: \n\n\u003cvuxml xmlns=\"http://www.vuxml.org/apps/vuxml-1\"\u003e\n   \u003cvuln vid=\"40bfcec7-807c-4fe8-92c6-8791d0e6589e\"\u003e\n     \u003ctopic\u003effmpeg -- FFmpeg vmd_read_header VMD File Integer Overflow\u003c/topic\u003e\n     \u003caffects\u003e\n       \u003cpackage\u003e\n         \u003cname\u003effmpeg\u003c/name\u003e\n         \u003crange\u003e\u003ceq\u003e\u003c/eq\u003e\u003c/range\u003e\n       \u003c/package\u003e\n     \u003c/affects\u003e\n     \u003cdescription\u003e\n       \u003cbody xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"\u003e\n         \u003cp\u003eVendor reports:\u003c/p\u003e\n         \u003cblockquote cite=\"http://git.ffmpeg.org/?p=ffmpega=commith=ebbccbaa5e925c2ddb212559f82c29ef526cc17e\"\u003e\n           \u003cp\u003eThe application is exposed to an integer overflow issue\nthat exists in the vmd_read_header of the\nlibavformat/sierravmd.c source file.\u003c/p\u003e\n         \u003c/blockquote\u003e\n       \u003c/body\u003e\n     \u003c/description\u003e\n     \u003creferences\u003e\n      \u003curl\u003ehttp://git.ffmpeg.org/?p=ffmpega=commith=ebbccbaa5e925c2ddb212559f82c29ef526cc17e\u003c/url\u003e\n     \u003c/references\u003e\n     \u003cdates\u003e\n       \u003cdiscovery\u003e2009-09-14\u003c/discovery\u003e\n       \u003centry\u003e2009-09-27\u003c/entry\u003e\n     \u003c/dates\u003e\n   \u003c/vuln\u003e"
